(2085, 'mobile-suit-sd-gundam-mk-ii', 2, 3, 10, 'Mobile Suit SD Gundam Mk. II delivers with more tongue-in-cheek humor than the first series. In \"The Rolling Colony Affair,\" a colony is hosting a cabaret show featuring the girls of Gundam. But the show turns disastrous when men and mobile suits go crazy over the girls, sending the colony rolling out of control. A parody of the videogame RPG genre, \"Gundam Legend\" has Amuro, Kamille and Judau sent on a perilous quest to rescue the princess of the Zeta Kingdom from Char Aznable and his vicious Zeon MS forces. rn(Source: ANN)', '', '2013-02-20 19:33:01', '2016-07-04 03:02:59', 'N', 'N', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3.317487448412227, 186, 'Teens 13 or older', 3, '1989-06-25', '1989-06-25', 0, '2085.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 56557),
