(2258, 'mei-and-the-baby-cat-bus', 1, 1, 14, 'This is a short film about 14 minutes long, which was shown for a limited time only at the Ghibli Museum. It tells the story of Mei and her friend the kittenbus (the child of the original catbus from My Neighbor Totoro). Mei is just small enough to ride in the kittenbus, which is only big enough to stir up dust devils, rather than making whole fields of rice sway in its breeze. One night they have an adventure in which they fly into the forest with many other cat-based vehicles, including many buses and trains. There they meet Totoro and many similar spirits, all heading for a gigantic catliner. This liner cruises off into the sky and the kittenbus takes Mei home.n (Source: AniDB)', 'N', '2013-02-20 19:35:28', '2016-07-04 03:03:05', 'Page2_large.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 134420, '2014-11-29 00:17:39', 3.686284038023146, 589, 'All Ages', 2, '2002-10-01', '0000-00-00', 0, '2258.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en', 'N', 28459),
(2259, 'onegai-my-melody', 2, 52, 24, 'My Melody arrives on Earth much to the surprise of her rival Kuromi. Together with one of the junior high school students, Yumeno Uta, they decide to protect the dreams of the people with the help of magic.', 'N', '2013-02-20 19:35:29', '2016-07-04 03:03:05', 'N', 'N', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3.48229146880559, 187, 'Children', 1, '2005-04-03', '2006-03-26', 0, '2259.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 57640),
(2272, 'ringetsu-the-animation', 4, 3, 30, 'Long time ago, the Rindo family was cursed by a monster. Since then, new born babies have been girls. To break the curse, they had to marry persons of the Higetsu family who have strong spiritual power, and have to bear a child by the next red moon. Now, the curse befalls to Rindo Naoto. In order to break the curse, he has to beget a child with one of four sisters of the Higetsus.n(Source: AnimeNfo)', 'N', '2013-02-20 19:35:42', '2016-07-04 03:03:06', 'N', 'N', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3.565274745185597, 159, 'Hentai', 3, '2006-07-25', '2006-09-25', 0, '2272.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 44312),
