(3572, 'xpress-train', 4, 2, 30, 'Kazuo Sugimoto is your typical young salaryman until he is wrongfully accused of molesting a girl on a train and forced to confess. After finding and confronting the true culprit, Kazuo becomes the man\'s 500th apprentice in Chikan-do: The Way of the Groper. Follow Kazuo\'s saga as he learns strategies such as The Berlin Wall, The Battle of Odawara and works to master his own technique The Gold Finger. Chikan-do: It will change the way you think.', 'N', '2013-02-20 19:54:54', '2016-07-04 03:04:10', 'N', 'N', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3.4146351891264284, 106, 'Hentai', 3, '2003-02-14', '2003-05-09', 0, '3572.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 48989),
(3579, 'the-melancholy-of-haruhi-suzumiya-2009', 2, 14, 24, 'The new episodes of the \"2nd season\" of Haruhi Suzumiya aired in chronological order along with the re-airing of The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya 2006 in what is called according to Kyoto Animation: The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya 2009. rnThis season contains arcs that occurred chronologically in the first season and more.', '', '2013-02-20 19:55:00', '2016-07-04 03:04:10', 'Haruhi-Yuki-and-Mikuru-in-yukatas-the-melancholy-of-haruhi-suzumiya-32257867-1920-1080.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 684385, '2014-11-17 01:13:13', 3.6534581406158844, 16521, 'Teens 13 or older', 1, '2009-05-22', '2009-09-11', 0, 'tumblr_o7utnjkE9w1ronjxdo1_1280.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2016, 90, 0, 0, 'en', 'N', 139581),
