(4564, 'tegami-bachi-letter-bee', 2, 25, 20, 'Apparently abandoned by his mother, orphan Lag Seeing is taken as a \"letter\" by \"Letter Bee\" Gauche Suede to a town where his aunt raises him. His affection and admiration for Gauche give Lag the ambition to become a Letter Bee himself, carrying mail through the dangerous wasteland between towns on his world. When he becomes a teenager, he makes the trip to the capital to take the examination to become a trainee Letter Bee. En route, he meets the strange, powerful girl-like creature Niche, who becomes his \"dingo,\" a Letter Bee\'s travelling companion. Lag yearns to find his mother, and discover why she abandoned him, if she did.rn[Source: ANN]', '', '2013-02-20 20:10:10', '2016-07-04 03:04:53', '0b40e9c5b9.png', 'image/png', 3101669, '2014-12-08 16:51:54', 3.767381973995344, 3972, 'Teens 13 or older', 1, '2009-10-03', '2010-03-27', 0, '4564.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en', 'N', 44158),
