(7278, 'date-a-live', 3, 12, 23, 'Itsuka Shido is a high school boy. On the last day of the spring holidays, an explosion destroys the town and a girl in armor appears in front of him. Shido\'s sister-in-law, Kotori, tells him that the girl is called \"Special Disasterous Designated Creature: Spirit\", which causes a timespace quake. Kotori disclosed that she is the commander of the anti-spirit organization Ratatosk and orders him to go out on a date with the spirit girl. Kotori says, \"I don\'t ask you to beat the spirit. Just let her fall in love with you and save the world.\"nn(Source: MAL)', 'VkI8QZpHnjk', '2013-02-20 20:53:12', '2016-07-04 03:06:56', '402690.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 173913, '2014-11-18 03:23:08', 3.6373676905995223, 15618, 'Mild Nudity', 1, '2013-04-06', '2013-06-22', 0, '7278.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 100, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 122972),
(7288, 'phi-brain-kami-no-puzzle-shukuteki-ratsel-hen', 2, 25, 22, '\"Are puzzles really necessary in this world?\"nnIn order to restore Jin\'s memory, Kaito and his friends go on a puzzle-viewing journey to England. As they\'re walking through the underground maze beneath the church, where young Kaito and Rook first met Jin, a mysterious girl appears in front of them.nnJin calls the girl by the name \"Raetsel\". It seems they know each other. However, she suddenly disappears and takes Jin with her. What\'s more, the traps in the underground maze are activated and start coming after Kaito and his friends.nn(Source: NHK)', '29MO3RU52Xc', '2013-02-20 20:53:22', '2016-07-04 03:06:56', 'N', 'N', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3.692554776658196, 1410, 'Teens 13 or older', 1, '2013-10-06', '2014-03-23', 0, 'Phi-Brain-Season-3-Key-Visual1.png', 'image/png', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 961494),
