(7366, 'toaru-kagaku-no-railgun-s', 3, 24, 24, 'The second season will focus on The Sisters Arc. Lasting only a single volume in the Toaru Majutsu no Index light novels, it was later expanded greatly in the Toaru Kagaku no Railgun manga.nThe arc focuses on the ordeals of Mikoto Misaka after discovering the existence of the Radio Noise sisters that are being used in the Level 6 Shift, an experiment where they are killed in order for the highest-ranking Level 5, Accelerator, to achieve Level 6.n(Source: Wikipedia)', '28m2UBZ91nQ', '2013-02-20 20:54:42', '2016-07-04 03:07:02', 'misaka_20mikoto__20to_20aru_20kagaku_20no_20railgun__20to_20aru_20majutsu_20no_20index.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 1185892, '2014-12-17 17:54:38', 4.177477396337765, 11654, 'Violence, Profanity', 1, '2013-04-12', '2013-09-27', 0, '001.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 170, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 593667),
(7370, 'nagi-no-asukara', 2, 26, 23, 'Long ago, all humans lived in the ocean. But some who longed for the land abandoned the ocean, casting off the special raiments granted to them by the sea god to adapt them to life under the sea...nnThough mankind was divided into sea dwellers and land dwellers, each with different ways of thinking, they were all still fellow humans, and they continued to maintain contact as time went on.nnSakishima Hikari, Mukaido Manaka, Hiradaira Chisaki, and Isaki Kaname live in an undersea village, while Kihara Tsumugu lives on land.nnWhen these middle school second-year land and sea dwellers meet for the first time, their hearts begin to undulate like the tides.nnThe youthful fantasy tale of these young people\'s lives unfolds in a strange and beautiful world.nn(Source: Crunchyroll)', 'dyHTarWe3gI', '2013-02-20 20:54:46', '2016-07-21 09:10:09', 'Nagi-no-Asakura.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 513140, '2016-06-07 15:01:52', 4.11743319425415, 14081, 'Teens 13 or older', 1, '2013-10-03', '2014-04-03', 0, 'naginoasukara.png', 'image/png', 0, 2015, 90, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 1468374),
