(7627, 'code-geass-oz-the-reflection-picture-drama', 2, 5, 3, 'Code Geass: Oz the Reflection (コードギアス 双貌のオズ, Kōdo Giasu: Sōbō no Ozu) is a spinoff published in Hobby Japan magazine and Kadokawa Shoten\'s Newtype Ace magazine. It tells a story from the viewpoints of two different protagonists, written by Shigeru Morita (Code Geass: Akito the Exiled, A Dark Rabbit Has Seven Lives) of Studio Nue. Bandai\'s Collectors division will turn the KMFs in Oz the Reflection into Robot Tamashii (Side KMF) figures, and Bandai\'s Hobby division will also release a 1/35-scale plastic model kit of the KMF Alexander from the Code Geass: Akito the Exiled anime project.nn(Source: Code Geass Wiki)', '', '2013-02-20 20:58:57', '2016-07-04 03:07:14', 'Picture_Drama_12.59_-1.png', 'image/png', 1180516, '2014-11-21 16:53:01', 3.212078896661937, 475, 'Teens 13 or older', 3, '2013-01-10', '0000-00-00', 0, '7627.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en', 'N', 13874),
