(7705, 'chuunibyou-demo-koi-ga-shitai-ren', 2, 12, 24, 'Due to various events, Yuuta and Rikka are living together. This secret co-habitation is so exciting for the two lovebirds! Or so it should be...nnIs having a chuuni girlfriend too high of a hurdle for Yuuta, who never even went out with a normal girl?!nnYuuta worries about how to advance his relationship with Rikka.nnAnd then everyone else, Nibutani, Kumin, and Dekomori, have powered up by advancing a grade.nnFurthermore, the cause of his chuunibyou outburst in middle school, the girl who calls herself Sophia Ring Saturn the 7th, Satone Shichimiya appears...nnThis is the long-awaited second season of the adolescent romantic comedy revolving around chuunibyou that makes you laugh and cry.', '', '2013-05-11 13:01:00', '2016-07-21 09:10:01', 'bX4p1B4.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 471776, '2014-11-21 16:48:09', 3.689158192376355, 12716, 'Teens 13 or older', 1, '2014-01-09', '2014-03-27', 0, 'iL7yNUtyrS0Kp.png', 'image/png', 0, 2015, 110, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 673999),
