(7731, 'kanojo-x-kanojo-x-kanojo-full', 4, 1, 90, 'A release of all 3 episodes of Kanojo x Kanojo x Kanojo compiled into 1 episode with some minor modifications such as additional changed view points during the h-scenes and the addition of a short h-scene of Midori Byakudan not found in the original part of episode 3.nHaruomi lives peacefully on a small island. But one day, a volcano erupts, so he gets out of the island and temporarily stays at his relative\'s house. He meets Natsumi, Akina, and Mafuyu there. They are sisters and all pretty. His peaceful life suddenly turns into an exciting erotic life....', '', '2013-05-23 03:22:22', '2016-07-04 03:07:20', 'N', 'N', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3.739039993329097, 317, 'Hentai', 3, '2013-04-19', '0000-00-00', 0, 'xJtWVmU.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2015, 0, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 206145),
