(7986, 'psycho-pass-movie', 3, 1, 114, 'Year 2116 – The Japanese government begins to export the Sibyl System unmanned drone robots to troubled countries, and the system spreads throughout the world. A state in the midst of a civil war, SEAUn (the South East Asia Union), brings in the Sibyl System as an experiment. Under the new system, the coastal town of Shambala Float achieves temporary peace and safety. But then SEAUn sends terrorists to Japan. They slip through the Sibyl System and then attack from within. The shadow of a certain man falls on this incident. In charge of the police, Tsunemori travels to Shambala Float to investigate. The truth of justice on this new ground will become clear.rnrn(Source: ANN)', '-6QwLSYmw98', '2013-09-07 02:53:27', '2016-07-04 03:07:29', 'MNlIuz3.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 200128, '2015-07-27 15:24:05', 4.0423362078866365, 5892, 'Violence, Profanity', 5, '2015-01-09', '0000-00-00', 0, 'ipBkNR7WWF2vK.png', 'image/png', 0, 2014, 67, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 1050517),
(8010, 'youkai-watch', 1, 0, 23, 'While walking around town one day, 5th grader Amano Keita notices a bizarre capsule toy machine in the woods and decides to buy a toy. But when he opens the capsule he receives, a ghostly creature named Whisper materializes. Impressed that Keita neither ran away nor bombarded him with questions, he decides to give Keita the Youkai Watch. The watch is a device that allows the wearer to see youkai, which are fantastical creatures, each type possessing different kinds of magical abilities, and which are normally invisible to humans. The Youkai Watch also allows the wearer to summon any youkai he has befriended, enabling the wearer to make use of the youkai\'s powers. Using it, Keita and Whisper encounter many mischievous youkai around town, resolving the trouble they\'re causing and befriending many at the same time.rnrn(Source: MU)', '', '2013-09-15 17:36:03', '2016-07-04 03:07:30', '275582-1.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 423214, '2016-02-26 23:15:58', 3.809146993204018, 461, 'All Ages', 1, '2014-01-08', '0000-00-00', 0, '275582-2.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2016, 250, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 263058),
(8018, 'aru-zombie-shoujo-no-sainan', 0, 0, 0, 'The story revolves around a beautiful girl named Euphrosyne (Yūfurojiinu) who is regretfully a zombie. Yūfurojiinu wakes up in an underground archive of a university, where a maid named Aruma tells her, \"Madam, kill the students and retrieve the \'Secret Stone.\'\"', 'vVXgEyMo7AQ', '2013-09-16 05:11:25', '2014-11-16 22:21:10', 'N', 'N', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 757, '', 1, '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 0, 'coverImage_48345.png', 'image/png', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 835830),
(8029, 'yuusha-ni-narenakatta-ore-wa-shibushibu-shuushoku-wo-ketsui-shimashita-ova', 3, 1, 25, 'In the story, a boy named Rauru did not get a chance to become a Hero, since the demon lord was already defeated just before his Hero exams. His dreams dashed, Rauru spends his days working at a magic shop in the capital. One day, a part-time job seeker appears at the shop with an amazing résumé. The work comedy revolves around this former Hero-in-training and the daughter of the demon lord. (Source: ANN)', '', '2013-09-22 21:08:10', '2016-07-04 03:07:31', 'N', 'N', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 3.386793996202513, 1586, '', 3, '2014-03-07', '2014-03-07', 0, 'fa47712025759066dd55bbfca7909a5c.png', 'image/png', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 381346),
