(9969, 'death-parade', 3, 12, 24, 'Quin Decim is a bar in a corner of the world where the souls of dead people gather. Gray-haired bartender Decim is responsible for judging the souls.nn“Welcome to Quin Decim.”nnWith no idea that they have died, two souls walk into the bar. Decim welcomes the customers, who are clueless as to what is going on. “I\'m going to ask you to bet your life and play games,” he declares. The souls must put their best efforts into playing various games for a chance to get out of the bar. Judgment will be based on the outcome of the games. As the games unfold, the souls\' true colors are bared. At the end, Decim finally reveals that he is the judge. What judgment will he hand down to the two?nnVarious views on life and a spectrum of sorrows surface from the judged souls, and as he experiences these emotions with Dark-haired woman, the usually emotionless Decim begins to feel changes within himself.nnWhat is life really all about? What is man\'s true nature? The story unfolds as it poses these questions.', 'n9lr8jqI-24', '2014-10-31 22:23:07', '2016-07-21 09:09:31', 'Death-Billiards-Anime.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 280194, '2015-02-06 03:09:49', 4.241325641852618, 17666, 'Violence, Profanity', 1, '2015-01-09', '2015-03-27', 0, 'isJvqja8CQ18j.png', 'image/png', 0, 2015, 150, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 865898),
(9971, 'fastening-days', 1, 1, 11, 'Yoji and Kei, a boy and girl,  live in a town in the not-so-distant future with their foster parent, Anna. But these seemingly ordinary children have a secret hidden even from their unsuspecting mother.rnrnYoji and Kei are superhero defenders of their town! With a flap of their capes, the two of them and their robot bear sidekick,  Oscar, protect the citizens in their town with their handmade high-tech machinery. But from what menace? And will our little heroes be able to overcome the  crisis about to threaten the town\'s peaceful everyday serenity?rnrnCheck out this utterly electrifying near-future animation to find out!rnrn(Source: Official website)', 'N', '2014-11-02 20:51:32', '2016-07-04 03:08:59', 'tumblr_ne9flbbT0F1rb1rgoo9_1280.png', 'image/png', 1734513, '2014-11-19 05:54:16', 3.3954935604897516, 261, 'All Ages', 4, '2014-10-30', '0000-00-00', 0, '68209.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2014, 0, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 22701),
