(11557, 'ghost-in-the-shell-the-new-movie-virtual-reality-diver', 2, 1, 10, 'Animation studio Production I.G announced that it will enter the virtual reality (VR) content market with an app titled Koukaku Kidoutai Shin Gekijou-ban Virtual Reality Diver (Ghost in the Shell: The New Movie Virtual Reality Diver).rnrnThe app will offer an original story in 360° 3D video, which can be seen with a VR headset. A three-minute promotional video will be available worldwide for the Oculus Rift on Google Play and App Store, followed by the full 10-minute work this winter.rnrn(Source: ANN)', 'HZ5py_n30to', '2015-11-24 19:07:25', '2015-12-28 01:20:48', 'N', 'N', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 122, 'Teens 13 or older', 2, '2016-02-01', '0000-00-00', 0, '4233fd640e6243e34bf3b3d9eb6c9945.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2015, 0, 0, 0, 'en', 'N', 310738),
(11560, 'reikenzan-hoshikuzu-tachi-no-utage', 2, 12, 24, 'In the anime\'s story, a comet falling will bring about a great calamity, and in order to choose a child fated by the falling comet, the family of the \"Reiken\" clan with a long storied history is once again resuming its entrance examination process to find disciples. The protagonist, who possesses a special soul that is only available once in a thousand years, decides to take the exam, and he starts down the path toward becoming an exceptional sage.rnrn(Source: ANN)', 'iqfZngrLWtI', '2015-11-26 03:54:51', '2016-07-04 03:10:50', '2bb18713dee2bb2041dc583910211856.png', 'image/png', 627662, '2016-02-15 08:37:26', 3.6626492981110186, 989, '', 1, '2016-01-09', '2016-03-26', 0, 'JJUJFqh.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 0, 2015, 200, 0, 0, 'en_jp', 'N', 271212),
